title: History Of Rockstar Games
description:
A look back at the first 25 years of Rockstar Games.

Not content with just releasing some of the best rated and best-selling games ever made, Rockstar Games has influenced and permeated pop culture like few before it. To celebrate its 25th anniversary, as well as the unveiling of the new Grand Theft Auto, here’s a look at the history of Rockstar.
